# gstack-codex

Codex-native migration of gstack with eight workflow skills and direct `agent-browser` command integration.

## Requirements

- Python 3.11+
- `uv`
- `agent-browser` installed and initialized:

```bash
npm install -g agent-browser
agent-browser install
```

## Quick Start

```bash
uv sync --dev
uv run gstack-codex doctor
uv run pytest
```

## Layout

- `.agents/skills/` Codex skills (`SKILL.md`)
- `src/gstack_codex/` Python core logic and command runner
- `tests/` unit, integration, and e2e-style smoke tests
- `docs/` migration and runbook docs
